                "original_url": "https:\/\/llllllll.co\/t\/experimental-music-notation-resources\/149",
                "fallback": "lines: Experimental music notation resources",
                "text": "As somebody with one foot in the visual art world and the other in sound world, I have always been interested in the experimental music notation strategies. Aside from the fact that these are often beautiful artifacts, I love thinking about the “utility” of images: how\/when image becomes an “instruction”. I think the new |||||||| forum, with it’s expanded conceptual ambition, ought to have a thread devoted to this aspect of new and experimental music. Let’s share resources, files, images, link...",
